  "releaseHighlights": "- Significant performance improvements on CUDA systems, up to 3.9x faster.\n- Improved performance on Metal.\n- Added support for 1000 series Nvidia GPUs.\n- Added a new smart scheduler for a balanced refresh rate in the viewer and playback.\n- Enabled dynamic updates even when the plugin is on the clip level.\n- Improved visibility with larger point sizes and denser plots.\n- Organized the settings tab.\n- Added new default and preset options for user customization.\n- Added a saturation slider to control how colorful the plot is.\n- Added a snap to orthogonal view hot key \"s\"\n- Added experimental Gloss view plotting mode\n-Fixed the scheduler for better rerponse to updateas",
